title: Ep. #25 | SEVENTEEN, JANG BEOM JUNE, AND CELEB FIVE
description:
Miss us, Daebak Fam? This week, we cover Seventeen’s “FEAR”, Jang Beom June’s “EVERY MOMENT WITH YOU”, and Celeb Five’s “I WISH I COULD UNSEE THAT”.

Listen and learn about Eric’s shady snail business and his janky soccer mom car days. What kind of summer camps did your parents force you to join? Hopefully they were more enjoyable than Eric’s chess and debate camp.

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave us a comment, rating and/or review on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Soundcloud, or YouTube.

Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios

Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at https://divestudios.io/show/daebakshow/!
